| Is DVORAK Gaining Traction Among Coders?                           |
|   from the slow-news-day dept.                                     |
|   posted by Cliff on Saturday April 14, @20:32 (Input Devices)     |
|   http://ask.slashdot.org/article.pl?sid=07/04/15/0043237          |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

[0]coderpath asks: "At a recent [1]Seattle Ruby Brigade hack night
someone asked how many people used the DVORAK keyboard layout. Out of 9
people, 7 used DVORAK and only 2 were using QWERTY. I personally made the
switch last Christmas, after 25 years of typing with QWERTY. What do you
use? Have you switched to DVORAK? Have you been wanting to make the
switch? Has anyone else noticed an increase in adoption of DVORAK
lately?"

Discuss this story at:
    http://ask.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=07/04/15/0043237

Links:
    0. http://coderpath.com/
    1. http://www.zenspider.com/seattle.rb


