[0]NickFitz writes "Students at UCSC have [1]recreated the first level of
Donkey Kong using 6,400 Post-it notes stuck to the windows of the E2
building. It took a team of about 10 people five hours to complete the
work, which will remain in place until May 1. There's a [2]time-lapse
video of the construction process."

